%% Sequence Diagram - RAG_ONLY Flow
%% Data: 2026-07-23 (revisão corretiva)
%% Fluxo: RAG_ONLY (1 embedding + 1 S3 Vectors query + 1 generate)
%% Intents: INT-010, INT-013, INT-019, INT-020
%% Fonte: marh_feature_knowledge.md
%% Modelo: PROPOSED_PENDING_ACCOUNT_VALIDATION

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant MARH as API MARH
    participant Lambda as Lambda Agent
    participant Classifier as Classificador
    participant Bedrock as Bedrock<br/>(modelo confirmado)
    participant S3V as S3 Vectors
    participant S3 as S3 Docs

    MARH->>Lambda: InvokeFunction (mensagem: "O que é o MARH?")
    activate Lambda

    Lambda->>Lambda: Parse + Validação contexto
    Lambda->>Classifier: classify_deterministic(mensagem)
    activate Classifier
    Classifier-->>Lambda: intent=INT-019, flow=RAG_ONLY
    deactivate Classifier

    %% Generate embedding for query
    Lambda->>Bedrock: InvokeModel(embedding_model, "O que é o MARH?")
    activate Bedrock
    Bedrock-->>Lambda: query_vector[]
    deactivate Bedrock

    %% Query S3 Vectors directly
    Lambda->>S3V: QueryVectors(query_vector, topK=ASSUMPTION_REQUIRES_EVALUATION)
    activate S3V
    S3V-->>Lambda: matches + scores
    deactivate S3V

    %% Get chunks from S3
    Lambda->>S3: GetObject(chunks above threshold)
    activate S3
    S3-->>Lambda: chunk content
    deactivate S3

    alt Chunks acima do threshold (ASSUMPTION_REQUIRES_EVALUATION)
        Lambda->>Lambda: Monta prompt (system + context limitado + user)

        Note over Lambda: System: "Responda APENAS com<br/>base no contexto fornecido"<br/>Context: [chunks relevantes]<br/>User: mensagem original

        Lambda->>Bedrock: InvokeModel(generation_model, prompt)
        activate Bedrock
        Bedrock-->>Lambda: Resposta gerada
        deactivate Bedrock

        Lambda->>Lambda: Validação de output (PII re-scan)
        Lambda-->>MARH: Response 200 (resposta informativa)
    else Nenhum chunk acima do threshold
        Lambda-->>MARH: Response 200 (ERR-008 sem LLM)
    end

    deactivate Lambda

    Note over MARH,S3: Latência: ASSUMPTION_REQUIRES_LOAD_TEST<br/>LLM: 1 embedding + 1 geração<br/>Fonte: marh_feature_knowledge.md
